AFN BULLBAR TO SUIT FORD RANGER PXII (2015 – 2017)

AFN bullbar to suit Ford Ranger PXII (2015 – 2017) available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The pictured bullbar features;

  • Full Bumper Replacement
  • Rated Recovery Points
  • Dual Antenna Tabs
  • Winch Compatible
  • Hi-Lift Jack Points
  • Fog/Indicator Light Assemblies
  • Satin Black Powder Coated

PLEASE NOTE: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order. 

CLICK HERE to view the range of products available for your Ford Ranger!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
